        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>equipment spaces [300103941], rooms and spaces by function [300004021], rooms and spaces [300133704], built work divisions [300072553], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
